# Quick Start Guide

## Project: alu_regex-data-extraction-{YourUsername}

### Overview
This is a complete solution for the "Data Extraction & Secure Validation Assignment" that implements regex-based data extraction with comprehensive security validation.

### Quick Run

```bash
# 1. Extract data from sample input
python3 data_extractor.py

# 2. Run security tests
python3 test_malicious_input.py

# 3. Demo HTML tag extraction
python3 demo_html_extraction.py
```

### Files Included

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `data_extractor.py` | Main program with all extraction logic |
| `sample_input.txt` | Realistic sample input (customer service logs) |
| `sample_input_with_html.txt` | Sample with HTML tags |
| `test_malicious_input.py` | Security validation test suite |
| `demo_html_extraction.py` | HTML tag extraction demo |
| `extraction_results.json` | Sample output (JSON format) |
| `SAMPLE_OUTPUT.txt` | Sample output (text format) |
| `README.md` | Comprehensive documentation |
| `.gitignore` | Git ignore file |

